41, apex of Ant. IV; 42, distal part of Ant. III; 43, distal part of Ant. II; 44, dorsal chaetotaxy of head; 45, labrum; 46, lateral process of labial palp; 47, labium; 48, maxillary outer lobe. Scale bars: 41−48 = 20μm.
